  "text": "Oxygen oxidation of model lignin solutions was also carried out with the aim of totally degrading and removing the lignin. The parameters of temperature, pH and reaction time showed the most significant degradation results with the effects of pressure not being as significant a parameter for the optimisation of lignin degradation [CITATION_1] .",
